 lang=\"EN-US\">,GDP26000</span></strong></em><em><strong><span>亿美元</span></strong></em><em><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">,“</span></strong></em><em><strong><span>市领导</span></strong></em><em><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">”6</span></strong></em><em><strong><span>人。东京</span></strong></em><em><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span></strong></em><em><strong><span>人口</span></strong></em><em><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">1300</span></strong></em><em><strong><span>万</span></strong></em><em><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">,GDP11000</span></strong></em><em><strong><span>亿美元</span></strong></em><em><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">,“</span></strong></em><em><strong><span>市领导</span></strong></em><em><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">”7</span></strong></em> <em><strong><span>人。中国铁岭市</span></strong></em><em><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span></strong></em><em><strong><span>人口</span></strong></em><em><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">300</span></strong></em><em><strong><span>万</span></strong></em><em><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">,GDP46</span></strong></em><em><strong><span>亿美元</span></strong></em><em><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span></strong></em><em><strong><span>人口是东京的五分之一、纽约的六分之一</span></strong></em><em><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">,GDP</span></strong></em><em><strong><span>是东京的</span></strong></em><em><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">0.1%</span></strong></em><em><strong><span>、纽约的</span></strong></em><em><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">0.18%,</span></strong></em><em><strong><span>但是</span></strong></em><em><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span></strong></em><em><strong><span>市领导</span></strong></em><em><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span></strong></em><em><strong><span>却</span></strong></em> <em><strong><span>有</span></strong></em><em><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">41</span></strong></em><em><strong><span>名</span></strong></em><em><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span></strong></em><em><strong><span>是东京和纽约的</span></strong></em><em><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span></strong></em><em><strong><span>倍。